⟨me muz farrekhtn⟩ dem tsvey un fertsik.

375
00:20:14,505 --> 00:20:18,290
 vu bin ikh gevezn in tsvey un fertsik? avek keyn...

376
00:20:18,403 --> 00:20:22,740
yo, in tsvey un fertsik bin ikh dokh avek keyn, keyn S-...

377
00:20:32,578 --> 00:20:35,170
⟨fertsik⟩ bin ikh gevezn...

378
00:20:36,180 --> 00:20:39,720
un- undz ho'mir shoyn UNK...

379
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:44,587
vu iz geven der NEXTer plats ven ir zent avek fun Rayshe? vu zent ir gegan?

380
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:45,820
take in f- tsvey un fertsik.

381
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:54,071
vos iz? in tsvey un f- dor- in tsvey un fertsik iz gevezn azoy: UNK ze'mir avek oyf, kh'hob aykh gezogt az s'iz gevorn der geto.

382
00:20:54,162 --> 00:20:56,293
iz gegangen mayn shvester

383
00:20:56,293 --> 00:20:59,403
un zi hot oysgearbet⟨n a, -arbet⟩ a pshepustke,

384
00:20:59,511 --> 00:21:05,670
un zi hot di pshepustke UNK gemakht far dem tatn un far der mame,

385
00:21:05,670 --> 00:21:11,637
un nokh dem far di shviger, far, fun, fun a bru- fun a bruder, di shviger mit a yingele,

386
00:21:11,847 --> 00:21:15,570
un i- mikh. mir ⟨FOUR,⟩, ze'mir geforn

387
00:21:15,570 --> 00:21:18,740
keyn SANDOMIERZ. SANDOMIERZ.

388
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:21,830
un fun SANDOMIERZ ze'mir UNK arayn keyn,

389
00:21:21,904 --> 00:21:25,190
 keyn Plantsh.

390
00:21:25,313 --> 00:21:26,997
ze'mir arayn keyn Plantsh,

391
00:21:26,997 --> 00:21:30,280
un in Plantsh ze'mir gevezn finef a halbn monat.

392
00:21:30,865 --> 00:21:33,069
f- dortn gekent zayn fray?

393
00:21:33,177 --> 00:21:37,750
⟨, z-⟩ dort iz geven take fray. s'iz geven a poylishe, dray poylishe POLICE-layt.

394
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:40,916
geven a kleyn shtetl. s'iz nisht tsugekumen keyn TRAIN,

395
00:21:40,956 --> 00:21:43,180
nor zamdn iz gevezn,

396
00:21:43,180 --> 00:21:51,380
un, hobn di, d- zey kenen, zey veln zikh shlepn mit CAR- mit TRU- mit CARS, mit TRUCKS keyn, iber di zamdn? s'iz geven hoykhe zamdn!

397
00:21:51,621 --> 00:21:56,182
hobn zey, hot men, undz ze'mir dort arayn in dem shtetl, Plantsh,

398
00:21:56,182 --> 00:21:58,420
un ze'mir dort geven finef a halbn monat.

399
00:21:58,860 --> 00:22:03,039
un nisht gornisht, keyn, m'hot nisht gezen keyn daytsh, m'hot nisht gezen keynemen.

400
00:22:03,653 --> 00:22:07,539
eyn ⟨mol tsayt⟩ iz gekumen... dos oykhet, dos g- oykhet iz gevorn.

401
00:22:07,539 --> 00:22:13,410
iz gevorn vayter a ⟨d- zey⟩ zenen arayngekumen mit f- ferd mit, vegn.

402
00:22:13,272 --> 00:22:15,308
ver? ver iz arayngekumen?

403
00:22:14,065 --> 00:22:15,324
di daytshn.

404
00:22:15,398 --> 00:22:19,968
un ongehoybn tsu zukhn JUDENREIN tsu zayn, s'zol zayn

405
00:22:19,968 --> 00:22:21,889
aroys- aroysgetribn di yidn.

406
00:22:22,182 --> 00:22:24,116
nu, mir, di eltern

407
00:22:24,223 --> 00:22:29,096
mit mayn take shvester vos zi hot gefirt, hot gemakht di pshepustkes,

408
00:22:29,096 --> 00:22:33,330
iz, iz ge- zi iz mitgeforn mit undz.

409
00:22:33,330 --> 00:22:38,561
zi hot dokh nisht gebroykht. azoy hot men gekent, ⟨ho'mir⟩ gehat a pshepustke oyf fir mentshn,

410
00:22:38,668 --> 00:22:40,158
fir mishpokhes.

411
00:22:40,158 --> 00:22:43,593
ho'mir azoy, azoy ze'mir geforn. ze'mir gekumen keyn Plantsh.

412
00:22:43,593 --> 00:22:48,078
nokh dem, di shvester mit mir zen- zi iz geforn vayter keyn Bokhnye,

413
00:22:48,118 --> 00:22:50,360
⟨un⟩ UNK zi hot dokh gehandlt;

414
00:22:50,360 --> 00:22:52,196
zi hot dokh gem⟨UNK⟩ parnose.

415
00:22:52,692 --> 00:23:01,022
iz, ⟨hot men z-⟩ iz d⟨- keyn P-⟩ iz zi avekgefo- zi iz geforn un nokh dem iz zi tsurikgekumen. yedes mol hot zi gegebn a kum tsurik

416
00:23:01,078 --> 00:23:02,928
un zi hot gebrengt UNK.

417
00:23:02,935 --> 00:23:10,470
un azoy arumet iz, mir ho'mir gelebt dort un m'hot ge- finef a halbn monat gegat ruik. m'hot nisht gevust...

418
00:23:09,212 --> 00:23:13,357
UNK ⟨un vi zent ir⟩ durkhgekumen mit di, mit di poylishe mentshn dortn?

419
00:23:12,469 --> 00:23:15,399
poylish⟨e⟩ UNK geven dray POLICE-layt in gantsn.

420
00:23:15,405 --> 00:23:23,431
nu, POLICE-layt, m'hot zey gegebn a por, raynish, a por dolar, iz er, iz er gegangen. ⟨, ot vet er geyn zukhn?⟩

421
00:23:23,252 --> 00:23:26,148
un vos hot pasirt ven s'zenen arayngekumen di doytshn?

422
00:23:25,986 --> 00:23:32,657
⟨d- az di⟩ doytshn zenen arayngekumen ze'mir, dervayl iz m- hot men shoyn zey ⟨g-⟩, zey zenen UNK gekumen oysgevizn,

423
00:23:32,657 --> 00:23:38,841
un ikh mit, mit der shvester take, di vos hot gemakht di, di, zi iz geven a blonde,

424
00:23:38,841 --> 00:23:43,684
ho'mir zikh bahaltn mitn... mir hobn nisht gerekhnt az s'kumt ver arayn,

425
00:23:43,684 --> 00:23:48,190
hot men undz ⟨z-⟩ mit eyn mol gekhapt. m'hot nisht gekhapt ⟨ze-⟩ avektsuzetsn,

426
00:23:48,190 --> 00:23:53,725
nor eyn mol azoy ⟨ho'mir ge- dos, ho'mir⟩ zikh bay nakht bahaltn, ven zey hobn, m'hot gehert az zey geyen

427
00:23:53,725 --> 00:23:57,772
ho'mir zikh bahaltn oyf a boydem bar a goy, a fotografist,

428
00:23:57,897 --> 00:23:58,920
un az...

429
00:23:58,015 --> 00:23:59,477
 vi hot er geheysn?

430
00:23:59,466 --> 00:24:00,320
ver?

431
00:24:00,023 --> 00:24:00,911
der goy.

432
00:24:00,833 --> 00:24:09,530
der goy veys ikh, ⟨, dos v- ikh ken,⟩ ken ikh nisht, vayl ikh bin dokh dort nisht ge- SPECIAL gevoynt, nor kh'bin gevezn dort mit mayn shvester, shve- hob ikh arayn dort.

433
00:24:09,658 --> 00:24:13,772
haklal, ⟨ze-⟩ ho'mir gehert, ze'mir gelegn oyfn boydem, ho'mir gehert

434
00:24:13,772 --> 00:24:15,266
vi di politsey,

435
00:24:15,266 --> 00:24:17,443
di daytshe, di daytshe POLICE,

436
00:24:17,443 --> 00:24:19,845
 ⟨n-⟩ redt mit dem goy,

437
00:24:20,020 --> 00:24:21,248
⟨un⟩ zogt er,

438
00:24:21,248 --> 00:24:24,755
⟨ot⟩ der goy hot gezogt ts- tsu zey, "HIER KEIN JUDE."

439
00:24:25,369 --> 00:24:27,219
"do gey- do iz nishto keyn yidn."

440
00:24:27,428 --> 00:24:33,716
azoy iz er avek, un zenen zey avekgegangen un d⟨UNK⟩. un der tate mit der mame mit der shvester

441
00:24:33,722 --> 00:24:37,000
mitn kind hot men mitgenumen keyn Stashev.

442
00:24:36,912 --> 00:24:38,644
ver hot mitgenumen zey?

443
00:24:37,958 --> 00:24:39,570
di daytshn.

444
00:24:39,662 --> 00:24:40,854
keyn Stashev.

445
00:24:41,299 --> 00:24:43,290
⟨un⟩ mir zenen dokh geven bahaltn.

446
00:24:43,290 --> 00:24:45,410
⟨un zi,⟩ mir, in der fri

447
00:24:45,410 --> 00:24:48,721
ho'mir bald ⟨g-⟩ avek fun, fun Plantsh

448
00:24:48,721 --> 00:24:55,502
un ze'mir gegangen keyn Pa-, keyn ⟨z-⟩ Pa- Patshenev, un zey zenen ge- zey hot men gefirt keyn Stashev.

449
00:24:55,626 --> 00:25:00,615
un azoy arumet hot ⟨mayn fot- iz men,⟩ iz men farloyrn gegangen

450
00:25:00,638 --> 00:25:01,900
mit di eltern,

451
00:25:02,106 --> 00:25:04,330
un mir zenen geforn biz Bokhnye.

452
00:25:05,211 --> 00:25:07,005
⟨in B- B-⟩ in Bokhnye,

453
00:25:07,005 --> 00:25:12,910
UNK BEFORE Bokhnye ze'mir geforn k-, m'iz geforn mit a koleyke, a kleyne shtot

454
00:25:12,910 --> 00:25:16,050
fun Stitshin biz, biz Bokhnye...

455
00:25:16,467 --> 00:25:18,674
biz Torne, TARNÓW...

456
00:25:18,674 --> 00:25:20,285
⟨ir hot⟩ gehert fun TARNÓW? ⟨yo?⟩...

457
00:25:20,285 --> 00:25:26,889
⟨in T- in⟩ TARNÓW. ⟨un in der⟩ TARNÓW iz a groyser STATION. s'iz geven a groyser farker.

458
00:25:27,165 --> 00:25:31,293
hobn, ze'mir aropgegangen, bin ikh g- shoyn gekumen mit a rebetsin,

459
00:25:31,907 --> 00:25:33,571
vayl in Patshenev

460
00:25:33,713 --> 00:25:38,764
hot, hot zi gezukht ⟨m- ah, m-⟩ mitts- mittsunemen a mentsh

461
00:25:38,764 --> 00:25:40,237
vos er zol zi hitn,

462
00:25:40,463 --> 00:25:42,915
un, un ikh UNK in Patshenev.

463
00:25:42,915 --> 00:25:48,150
in Patshenev iz nishto keyn ⟨T-⟩, iz nor geven zamd, arum un arum zamd.

464
00:25:48,343 --> 00:25:50,193
iz, hot zi gezogt,

465
00:25:50,368 --> 00:25:54,187
zi volt gevolt forn keyn Kro- zi ⟨hot gev- -darft⟩ tsu forn keyn Kroke.

466
00:25:54,187 --> 00:25:59,441
hot zi... nor vos den? zi hot moyre aleyn tsu forn. dervayl, ikh hob nisht gegat keyn PAPERS, GAR UNK

467
00:25:59,582 --> 00:26:01,905
GAR NIX! kh'hob nisht gehat keyn shum PAPER.

468
00:26:02,130 --> 00:26:04,132
zog ikh, "ikh vel mit aykh..."

469
00:26:02,923 --> 00:26:06,393
 vos hot pasirt tsu di papirn vos di shvester hot gemakht far aykh?

470
00:26:06,197 --> 00:26:11,160
nisht far mir. zi, ⟨dos, der pape-⟩ di PAPER iz dokh shoyn aroys. ⟨d- d-⟩ dokh aroys, ⟨zi iz dokh g-⟩

471
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:15,944
der T- der TRAIN iz dokh gevorn, dortn. zi, ⟨m-⟩ ikh bin shoyn geven in an anderer TRAIN.

472
00:26:16,120 --> 00:26:19,421
⟨hakl-,⟩ zi, di froy, zi iz a rebetsin gevezn,

473
00:26:19,545 --> 00:26:23,622
hot zi gezogt, zi hot gezukht a mentsh, zol mit z- zol mit ir forn.

474
00:26:23,713 --> 00:26:30,570
⟨ha⟩klal, ikh hob mikh geshtelt, un kh'hob nisht gehat keyn shum PAPER in der hant, vayl, poylishe hob ikh dokh nisht gegat shoyn.

475
00:26:30,570 --> 00:26:31,959
kh'hob shoyn oykhet nisht gegat.

476
00:26:32,067 --> 00:26:33,802
⟨ha⟩klal, vos, vos tut men?

477
00:26:33,802 --> 00:26:40,890
bin ikh gegangen un ikh hob mikh gemoldn mit⟨,⟩ az ikh for mit, mit ir mit. zogt zi, "OKAY," hot zikh gefreyt.

478
00:26:40,890 --> 00:26:42,787
ikh kum arunter fun Torne,

479
00:26:42,787 --> 00:26:46,859
un kh'gey arunter UNK. ⟨s'geyt undz antkegn⟩ a poylisher politsyant

480
00:26:46,883 --> 00:26:49,408
un er, un firt undz arayn tsu der GESTAPO.

481
00:26:50,983 --> 00:26:52,242
d⟨er za⟩kh!

482
00:26:52,536 --> 00:26:57,390
⟨haklal,⟩ farfaln. kumt, der poylisher p- UNK

483
00:26:57,390 --> 00:26:58,920
er iz ar- avekgegangen,

484
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:05,000
un di rebetsin iz geven vays vi, take vays UNK efsher vayser vi dos gloz!

485
00:27:05,192 --> 00:27:06,131
⟨un,...⟩

486
00:27:05,435 --> 00:27:06,910
vi hot zi geheysn?

487
00:27:06,559 --> 00:27:14,551
di rebetsin? a Krokever. ikh veys nisht. ikh ho- ikh hob zi afile nisht UNK. nor vos den? zi hot mi-, ikh hob, zi hot mikh ge- ayngetragn UNK az ikh zol mitforn.

488
00:27:14,727 --> 00:27:17,421
zi hot ge⟨vart far⟩ fir mentshn a pshepustke.

489
00:27:16,667 --> 00:27:18,838
vos hot pasirt in der GESTAPO?

490
00:27:18,912 --> 00:27:26,499
⟨okh, do- o, do, o.⟩ ⟨un der, ha⟩klal, ⟨un⟩ der poylisher politsyant nemt undz arayn un firt undz arayn tsu der GESTAPO.

491
00:27:27,130 --> 00:27:32,710
ikh shtey un ikh red un ikh red. i- ikh red daytsh, veyst ir dokh vi a yid hot geredt daytsh:

492
00:27:32,710 --> 00:27:40,660
"der VA- der VATER iz geforn friert vi azoy der onkl." UNK onkl, ikh, onkl vey- hob ikh shoyn gevust.

493
00:27:40,660 --> 00:27:48,870
UNK un ⟨shoyn⟩. un mit eyn mol heybt zikh oyf ⟨der, s'iz epes⟩ gekumen a, a VOICE fun oyvn, a kol,

494
00:27:49,033 --> 00:27:53,161
un, un mir, un mir zenen ⟨un-⟩ UNK tsitern.

495
00:27:53,573 --> 00:27:54,910
un me vart.

496
00:27:55,007 --> 00:27:59,300
zog ikh tsu der rebetsin, "kumt, lomir geyn! lomir geyn!"

497
00:27:59,783 --> 00:28:03,760
zi, ⟨ikh, zi hot,⟩ "!" zi hot nisht gekent iberredn a vort.

498
00:28:03,850 --> 00:28:10,060
haklal, UNK ikh hob zi aroysgeshlept un punkt, di TR- di TRAIN iz nokh geshtanen.

499
00:28:10,060 --> 00:28:13,462
undz ho'mir gegebn a gey arayn in der TRAIN un ze'mir avekgeforn.

500
00:28:13,671 --> 00:28:17,420
geven, der poylisher politsey iz dokh geshtanen dort oyf GUARD.

501
00:28:17,420 --> 00:28:25,440
er hot ober nisht gevust. az er hot gezen az me geyt aroys, hot er farshtanen, "efsher hot men zey bafrayt." ⟨ir farsht-⟩ az m'hot undz bafrayt UNK

502
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:31,350
ikh hob azoyne... un arayn in der TRAIN, iz di TRAIN sh- bald geforn, azoy vi ze'mir arayngekumen.

503
00:28:30,732 --> 00:28:33,125
undz darf'mir iberraysn oyf a por minut.

504
00:28:32,217 --> 00:28:33,030
yo.

